The code base contains two separate implementations of the function `quicksort_place`, one in lib/topfish/rescale_layout.c and one in lib/neatogen/kkutils.c. Both contain an optimization to avoid a recursive call when the chunk they’re sorting is already sorted. However the neatogen implementation additionally performs the two recursive calls before these checks:

